high_descs: Walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the tomato off of the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the tomato inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the tomato, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the chilled tomato inside to the right of the cup, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the tomato in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and take it out again.
Turn left and walk along the counter to the microwave.
Place the tomato in the microwave to the right of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Move forward and then to your right so you are facing the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a tomato from the counter
Turn around and then turn to your left to face the fridge
Open the fridge, put the tomato inside to chill for a few seconds and then pick it back up
Turn left twice so that you are in front of the microwave
Put the tomato inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Chill a tomato and put it in a microwave
